==Honours and awards==

HRH Prince Turki has been awarded [[Doctorate of Letters|Honorary Doctorate of Letters]](DLitt) of [http://www.swansea.ac.uk/ [[Swansea University]]] in June 2017 on receiving his award, HRH Prince Turki said: “I am absolutely delighted to have received this award from Swansea University. It is a real honour and privilege to work with a truly world-class institution that serves nations’ future leaders and communities with such passion.

I would like to take this opportunity to thank the University Council, School of Management, and the [http://www.swansea.ac.uk/alumni/ Development and Alumni Relations Office] for nominating me and I dedicate my award to the people of the [[Kingdom of Saudi Arabia]] and other nations."
